name: The Mist of Tang Sancai
description: "唐三彩之迷雾"/"The Mist of Tang Sancai" This is a copper etching print I made many years ago and I'm excited to bring it to you know in #NFT form. 三彩Sancai is a form of glazed pottery art from the 唐朝Tang Dynasty, Sancai literally means 3 colors. To see more of my art follow me on FB/IG @magpieartistry and on Twitter @ArtistryMagpie
